::Prowl::

Prowl puts away his gun, and walks off after Iron Raptor. "Ramhorn," he says 
into his comm-link, "I'm a bit busy right now."

With that, he reaches Iron Raptor, looking at her as she leans against the 
wall, aparently falling asleep. He looks her over. Maybe she did need sleep 
more than repairs.

Prowl sighs, taking Iron Raptor in his arms and lifting her. Looking down at 
her face, a soft look enters Prowl's optics and he kisses her before walking 
off toward her quarters.
